history.content:
Professor Hug posted a survey yesterday for students to fill out so the staff could hopefully try and expand the class! So please fill it out when you have the time, thanks :)

Here's the exact post:

"Given today's Daily Cal article about EECS having huge waitlists, I think there is some chance that we'll be able to find the money and political will to expand! In case you missed it, here it is: http://www.dailycal.org/2016/08/24/campus-budget-issue-prompts-concern-eecs-faculty-students-enrollment/

 

If you're on the waitlist (or you got off of it because the chances were too bad), please fill out this short survey: https://goo.gl/forms/B7eNcXzULgYTRLRl1

 

I can't promise anything, but I'll use the results to try to push for more resources and hopefully expand the class so that we can accommodate everyone who is strongly interested.

Feel free to pass on to other folks who may have abandoned our Piazza.

 

Thanks!

-Josh"
history.subject: CS188 Waitlist Survey (or if you're interested in taking the class this semester)
